<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101805034375917></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101805034375917><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=7&mid=101805034375917>RE: Wis</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=7&mid=101805034375917#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=153318><span id=Scholar>Nrewfin</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>17 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Apr 5th 6:50 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Small Wisdom Diety's..+2 wisdom.&nbsp;&nbsp;These are made my experience potters, trivial at level 135, made by combining A flask of water, sands of Ro, large block of clay, and a deity sketch in a pottery wheel, and fired in a kiln with a high quality firing sheet.  These rarely seem to be on auction in the East Commons area, maybe if you shout out that you are looking for the services of a master potter, you would get a response.  If you are by any chance playing on The Seventh Hammer, look me up, you can have mine.  I will be getting a better range item shortly via the 3rd Prayer Shawl quest ;)  Good luck, Be safe, *~Peace~*<br><br>Nrewfin Givinglife<br>52 Vicar of Brell<br>Officer ~ Explorers of the Realms<br>The Seventh Hammer<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
