	   <tr><td colspan=2>The one I have is called a 'small wisdom deity', a little purple doll with 2 or 3 wisdom (cant remember). This one is made by players using the pottery skill and they generally sell for about 100p, but I am a master potter so I made it myself for about 30p. The most expensive ingredient is 'sands of ro' which is dropped off sand giants and sell for 25-30p to players.<br><br>Then there are the deity specific idols but not all of those have +wis. If you're a dwarf I'm guessing you worship Brell and that version of the idol doesn't have wis.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
